title: PlayRadioPlay! - Hooray! PlayRadioPlay! [2007] --Rare
description:
PlayRadioPlay! is the project of Dan Hunter from Forth Worth, Texas. At the age of 19 and with only the very basics, he has already managed to leave a major mark on the music scene of today.

Creating sweet, indie electro-pop songs which often relate back to experiences he has gone through in the past, Dan manages to create instantly catchy songs and yet retain a personal side to many of them.

He is also know for having an extremely close relationship with fans and regularly chats with them on websites such as MySpace and AbsolutePunk.
